title: [Enemy Ship, Helm]
description: Situated across from a wheel and laced with coils of thick, braided hemp rope, a capstan is prepared to weigh or drop anchor.  A viciously barbed harpoon is tangled in a mess of nets near a short flight of stairs, with a wooden door at bottom leading to the quarters of the captain.  A dagger-pierced parchment on the door proclaims, "ENTER AT YOUR OWN RISK!"
